God is Greatest -RRB- during post - election unrest in <TIMEX3 tid="t9" type="DATE" value="2009">2009</TIMEX3> .
Foreign correspondents have largely been excluded from Syria since the protests escalated and the crackdown began .
A Syrian rights group said at least 560 civilians have been killed in the six - week - old uprising in support of demands for greater political freedom and action against corruption that has flourished under the Baath Party , in power since <TIMEX3 tid="t10" type="DATE" value="1963">1963</TIMEX3> .
The uprising , unthinkable only months ago , flared after mass protests toppled authoritarian leaders in Egypt and Tunisia .
Demonstrations spread in Bahrain and escalated to civil war in Libya .
