The government also has little influence as Assad , his family and the security apparatus has a stranglehold on power .
Syria blames armed groups for the violence .
On <TIMEX3 tid="t16" type="DATE" value="2011-04-29">Friday</TIMEX3> soldiers killed 19 people when they fired on protesters who were trying to enter Deraa from nearby villages in a show of solidarity , a medical source said .
Syrian rights groups put <TIMEX3 tid="t17" type="DATE" value="2011-04-29">Friday</TIMEX3> 's death toll at 62 .
